{"snp4.6:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.6 ","snp4.6:0.2":"Jarasutta ","snp4.6:1.1":"Appam vata jivitam idam, ","snp4.6:1.2":"Oram vassasatapi miyyati; ","snp4.6:1.3":"Yo cepi aticca jivati, ","snp4.6:1.4":"Atha kho so jarasapi miyyati. ","snp4.6:2.1":"Socanti jana mamayite, ","snp4.6:2.2":"Na hi santi nicca pariggaha; ","snp4.6:2.3":"Vinabhavasantamevidam, ","snp4.6:2.4":"Iti disva nagaramavase. ","snp4.6:3.1":"Maranenapi tam pahiyati, ","snp4.6:3.2":"Yam puriso mamidanti mannati; ","snp4.6:3.3":"Etampi viditva pandito, ","snp4.6:3.4":"Na mamattaya nametha mamako. ","snp4.6:4.1":"Supinena yathapi sangatam, ","snp4.6:4.2":"Patibuddho puriso na passati; ","snp4.6:4.3":"Evampi piyayitam janam, ","snp4.6:4.4":"Petam kalankatam na passati. ","snp4.6:5.1":"Ditthapi sutapi te jana, ","snp4.6:5.2":"Yesam namamidam pavuccati; ","snp4.6:5.3":"Namamyevavasissati, ","snp4.6:5.4":"Akkheyyam petassa jantuno. ","snp4.6:6.1":"Sokapparidevamaccharam, ","snp4.6:6.2":"Na jahanti giddha mamayite; ","snp4.6:6.3":"Tasma munayo pariggaham, ","snp4.6:6.4":"Hitva acarimsu khemadassino. ","snp4.6:7.1":"Patilinacarassa bhikkhuno, ","snp4.6:7.2":"Bhajamanassa vivittamasanam; ","snp4.6:7.3":"Samaggiyamahu tassa tam, ","snp4.6:7.4":"Yo attanam bhavane na dassaye. ","snp4.6:8.1":"Sabbattha muni anissito, ","snp4.6:8.2":"Na piyam kubbati nopi appiyam; ","snp4.6:8.3":"Tasmim paridevamaccharam, ","snp4.6:8.4":"Panne vari yatha na limpati. ","snp4.6:9.1":"Udabindu yathapi pokkhare, ","snp4.6:9.2":"Padume vari yatha na limpati; ","snp4.6:9.3":"Evam muni nopalimpati, ","snp4.6:9.4":"Yadidam ditthasutam mutesu va. ","snp4.6:10.1":"Dhono na hi tena mannati, ","snp4.6:10.2":"Yadidam ditthasutam mutesu va; ","snp4.6:10.3":"Nannena visuddhimicchati, ","snp4.6:10.4":"Na hi so rajjati no virajjatiti. ","snp4.6:10.5":"Jarasuttam chattham. "}